## ğŸ“… WEEK 2 â€” Routing, Guards & Lazy Loading

### âœ… Topics to Cover

| # | Topic | Level |
|---|-------|-------|
| 1 | Angular Router â€” Routes, RouterLink, RouterOutlet | Intermediate |
| 2 | Route Parameters & Query Params | Intermediate |
